    "Once the structure of the receptor (protein, DNA, etc.)",
    "is known, more can be done in order to better understand the properties of the target.",
    "For example, in 2021, Kozlovskii and Popov developed a deep learning approach to predict the binding site for small molecules on nucleic acids, DNA, and RNA, based on their 3D structures (Kozlovskii and Popov 2021).",
    "Their approach is called BiteNet N (https:// sites. skolt ech.",
